title._content: Black Woman At The Operation Push Expo Annual Convention. A Special Talkathon Was Set Up By A Local Black Radio Station In Chicago, 07/1973

description._content: Original Caption: Black Woman At The Operation Push Expo Annual Convention A Special Talkathon Was Set Up By A Local Black Radio Station In Chicago To Help Raise Money For The Organization. One Of The Aims Of Push Is To Open The World Of Business To Small Black Owned Businesses. The Rev.
